<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer | Section 8 Calculator"
  description="Important legal disclaimer about Section 8 Calculator — an educational tool providing estimates based on HUD data, not affiliated with any government agency."
>
  <article class="container prose" style="padding: 2.5rem 0 4rem; max-width: 42rem;">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>

    <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Educational Estimates Only</h2>
    <p>
      Section 8 Calculator provides <strong>educational estimates</strong> based on publicly
      available data from the U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development (HUD), including
      Fair Market Rents (FMR), Small Area Fair Market Rents (SAFMR), and income limits. These
      estimates are intended to help users understand the Section 8 Housing Choice Voucher program
      and are <strong>not official eligibility determinations</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2>Not a Government Agency</h2>
    <p>
      This website is <strong>not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to</strong> HUD,
      any Public Housing Authority (PHA), any state or local housing agency, or any other
      government entity. We do not process applications, issue vouchers, or manage waiting lists.
    </p>

    <h2>No Guarantee of Accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      While we strive to keep our data current and accurate, HUD income limits and Fair Market
      Rents change annually, and local PHAs may apply additional rules, preferences, and payment
      standards that our calculator cannot account for. <strong>Actual eligibility, voucher
      amounts, and program rules may differ</strong> from the estimates shown on this site.
    </p>

    <h2>Not Legal or Financial Advice</h2>
    <p>
      Nothing on this website constitutes legal advice, financial advice, or professional
      housing counseling. For official eligibility determinations, application assistance, or
      legal questions about your housing rights, please contact:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your <a href="https://www.hud.gov/program_offices/public_indian_housing/pha/contacts">local Public Housing Authority (PHA)</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.hud.gov/counseling">HUD-approved housing counseling agencies</a></li>
      <li>A qualified attorney or legal aid organization in your area</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>External Links</h2>
    <p>
      This site contains links to external websites operated by government agencies, nonprofits,
      and other third parties. We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or privacy
      practices of those sites. Inclusion of a link does not imply endorsement.
    </p>

    <h2>Use at Your Own Risk</h2>
    <p>
      By using Section 8 Calculator, you acknowledge that the information provided is for
      <strong>educational and informational purposes only</strong>. We make no warranties,
      express or implied, about the completeness, reliability, or suitability of the
      information. Any reliance you place on our estimates is strictly at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this disclaimer from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
      with an updated date.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/about/">About us</a> · <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a>
    </p>
